  "description": "<p>Designed for in-between years, when they've outgrown a kid\u2019s bike, but aren\u2019t quite ready for an adult bike. Built on Cannondale\u2019s trail-tested C3 alloy frame, the Trail 26\u201d is ready to provide years of service and vbe a pretty rad hand-me-down. Front suspension takes the edge off of rough trails, and softens landings when they get sendy. When it's time to head back up the hill, a solid gear range makes it easier.</p><ul><li>SmartForm C3 alloy frame, with stable hardtail geometry</li><li>SR Suntour NEX suspension fork has a preload adjuster and 63mm of travel</li><li>1x8 drive train pairs a 30T chain ring with an 11-34T cassette</li><li>microSHIFT groupset, with Pro Wheel crankset</li><li>Powerful Tektro mechanical disc brakes keep speed in check</li><li>Internal cable routing keeps things safe and clean</li><li>Kenda small block tires grip well on trails and pavement</li><li>Smooth rolling 26\u201d wheels</li><li>Designed for kids 9-13 years old</li><li>Bikes are covered by MEC's Rocksolid Guarantee and Bike Service Agreement. You can bring your bike to any MEC bike shop for free adjustments and minor maintenance for a year after purchase</li></ul>",
